{"tid":1658907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 香港到了最危急的時候, 他站出來了!","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T04:08:23.000Z","uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8182e19ea925b16f8f05c682665ff4b48d7b4a08","tid":1658907,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"大家好，我是梁耀忠。<br />\n<br />\n自1985年當選區議員後，轉眼我在葵芳邨已經扎根34年。<br />\n<br />\n葵芳邨自重建至今已二十多年，一直以來我們全心全意服務街坊，樂見社區環境一點一點地改善。看似簡單如爭取一道斑馬線，或是一座升降機，背後都盛載著街坊與我們共同付出的努力，也全賴街坊多年來對我們的信任與支持，葵芳邨才有著今天的新面貌。<br />\n<br />\n近幾個月來，不論是在街站，還是在網上，都有不少市民向我反映，他們對冷血不仁的政府以及前景未明的局勢感到不安。我們堅持相信，解鈴還需繫鈴人，問題源於政府無視民間的訴求，縱容警方濫權濫捕，肆意踐踏人權；更重要的是，一日政治制度不改變，香港沒有真正的民主選舉，即使撤換特首，社會局勢是不可能有所好轉的。<br />\n<br />\n經歷三十四個寒暑，我們服務街坊的初心從來未變，面對香港當前的困境，我們願與街坊同行，共度難關。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我已於十月十日報名參加來屆區議會選舉</span>，希望你能支持我，讓我們可繼續建設社區。<br />\n<br />\n#為街坊<br />\n#為社區<br />\n#繼續努力打拼<br />\n<br />\n====================<br />\n梁耀忠<br />\n2019年葵青區議會選舉 葵芳選區候選人<br />\n選舉廣告 | 自行制作 | 日期：2019年10月14日 | 1份<br />\n===================="},{"pid":"59d899c39b976f7dc24847714eaf87278d8ebb29","tid":1658907,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fe9a2bc8c4eb324a4495a9740e3086f65b3070c3","tid":1658907,"uid":120555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"ed0e646f81dde447ea0cfaa6f37182feac2d24b8","tid":1658907,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"唔撚想知<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"0282c538d87a48ba29a961ec24755d3ab1854dbb","tid":1658907,"uid":288830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n求手足幫忙推Post！！！"},{"pid":"eb128a1b3967165c51821e10b9d5d32c7d8b55f1","tid":1658907,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:54:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3b7f8afc19a7c33631027e395cc003f45174ddc9","tid":1658907,"uid":45246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"肯收檔未呀白頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191cb6718b8ecf9d425bc49e65a27f11daed6aea","tid":1658907,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"收皮啦白頭佬，仲要線香港人幾多鑊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f75194e6cdc47d70add1731031bb0f4b69e175","tid":1658907,"uid":55233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"9f50ffcadb8f47617ab7eab2d0f6e78b2f351cc2","tid":1658907,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2c1206b10afdad94ad3cae3d9262b0bbcf54b18","tid":1658907,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"食屎喇"},{"pid":"1e606bd54610e6dd5baf34f1898185a9ac54abbe","tid":1658907,"uid":294173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"e246e73030361b6d5a1cc09f17f1d954154fb1e5","tid":1658907,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed0e646f81dde447ea0cfaa6f37182feac2d24b8","tid":1658907,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"唔撚想知<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:56:32.000Z","msg":"但fb引起好大迴響<i